section.para:
In the first page you will have to enter some basic information:
	
		'Function Library' wizard information page
		
			
				
					
				
			
		
	
	
		the Library Name should be a class-name like identifier and it will be used to generate the class file containing your functions;
		the Source folder is the chosen Build-Path entry;
		the Package is the Java package where most of the generated output files will be placed;
		the Category Label will be the text shown in the Expression Editor categories list;
		the Category Description is an additional details regarding the category
		the Category Class is automatically suggested based on the chosen label;
		the automatic creation of sample methods and an example report;
